#container
  #header
    img(src='./assets/clique-logo.png')
  #nav-bar
  #center-zone.rounded-corners
    h2 Clique: Spectral Analysis Made Awesome
    p
      | Clique features a spectral analysis web application that can take
      | your data and find trends in variable groupings. Check back soon for
      | a better description of what this awesome tool can offer!
    p
      | The spectral analysis tool employs a three step process:
      ol
        li 
          | Data Purification: purges all bad data segments from the given input for use
          | and compatibility with the analyzer
        li
          | Analysis Specifications: provides options, customizations, and configurations for
          | the tool's data-crunching and output
        li
          | Reporting: spits back the relevant data analysis and graphical data
    div.centering-container
      
      span#browser-compat.ui-widget.ui-state-highlight.rounded-corners
  #purifier.main-section.rounded-corners
    h1.ui-dialog-titlebar.ui-widget-header.rounded-corners Data Purification
    h2 [P1] Choose your input method
    #file-select-input.parse-option.input-select.rounded-corners
      p [P1.2] Select / Drag a file with data:
      input#file-input(type="file")
      p#file-info
      #file-loading
        #loading-status
    #text-field-input.parse-option.input-select.rounded-corners
      p [P1.1] Input data into the text area:
      textarea#text-input(rows="10", cols="45")
    hr
    h2 [P2] Choose your configurations and options
    #delimiter-choice.parse-option.rounded-corners
      p [P2.1] Select delimiters in the data
      input#delimiter-comma(type="checkbox")
      label(for="delimiter-comma") Comma
      input#delimiter-space(type="checkbox")
      label(for="delimiter-space") Space
      input#delimiter-tab(type="checkbox")
      label(for="delimiter-tab") Tab
      br
      p Custom:
        input#delimiter-custom(type="text")
    hr
    div.centering-container  
      button#purify-button(disabled="true") Print Data
    h2 [Temporary] File printout
    #file-out
  #analyzer.main-section.rounded-corners
    h1.ui-dialog-titlebar.ui-widget-header.rounded-corners Spectral Analysis
    h2 [You must first purify your data before analyzing it]
  #results.main-section.rounded-corners
    h1.ui-dialog-titlebar.ui-widget-header.rounded-corners Results
    h2 [You must analyze your data before viewing any results]
